<!-- content starts here --> 
<font class="subhead2">Press and financial/market analysts should register for CES through the press registration form.  If you are a press or financial/market analyst, please <a href="/press/register_press.asp?menuItem=0&subMenuItem=-1&tabName=Press">visit the Press Registration area</a> of the site to register.</font><p>

<font class="subhead">Attendee Registration</font><p>


<font class="body">
Register now to receive your CES badge by mail. Avoid waiting in line...Register by November 17!<p>

All Advance Registration closes on December 15, 2000. On-site registration is $75 per person. (No one under the age of 16 is permitted on the show floor.)<p>

<font class="subhead2">Register for the Exhibits Plus Pass, it's FREE! This gives you access to all CES exhibits</font>. <p>

There are <b><font size="+1">3</font></b> easy ways to register:<p>
1. <b><!--<a href="https://register.rcsreg.com/regos-1.0/ces01/adv/ga/live/attendee.html">-->


<a href="https://register.rcsreg.com/regos-1.0/ces01/adv/ga/live/">Register online</a><!--- beginning July 1st--->.</b> Simply follow the instructions, <b>print your confirmation</b> and it's done.<p>

2. <b>Download a registration form</b>, fill it out and fax it to us for processing. Your registration will be processed within 10 business days. You can check the status of your registration online at any time after that.<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="domesticadvreg.pdf"><b>Download a registration form for General Attendees</b></a></li>
<li><a href="intladvreg.pdf"><b>Download a registration form for International Attendees</b></a> <br><a href="intlregpkg.asp">(Click here for a special offer for International Attendees!)</a><br><br></li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt><dd>
<table>
<tr><td valign=top><a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/acrobat/readstep.html"><img src="/global_images/getacro.gif" width=88 height=31 border=0 alt="Get the Adobe Acrobat Reader"></a></td><td><font class="body">These registration forms are in Adobe PDF format. You will need the Adobe Acrobat reader in order to view the files. Need the Acrobat Reader? <a href="http://www.adobe.com/products/acrobat/readstep.html">Click here.</a></font></td></tr>
</table>
</dd></dt>
</dl>
<br>
3. Get a registration form by fax.  Call our Fax-On-Demand service to request a registration form by fax.  Listen carefully to make sure you get the right form.  Hotel Reservation forms and other information also are available.<p>

In the U.S. call: 1 888 CES SHOW (237 7469)<br>
Outside the U.S. call: +1 732 544 2865<p>

Avoid waiting in line by registering NOW!! All Advance Registration closes on December 15, 2000. On-site registration is $75 per person. ($65 for international visitors)<p>

Questions? <a href="/contact.asp?emailSubject=Help">E-mail us</a> for help with your registration regardless of the method you choose, or call 703 907 7605.<p>

